Text.Value: What were you carrying in the wagons?

EditorData.NodeContext: After casting a speak with dead spell

Text.Value: *The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Rugan... protected it... took it... north...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*

EditorData.NodeContext: Our speak with dead spell runs out of power

Synopsis: Using a speak with dead spell, we are able to talk to the spirit of Amnos, a zhentarim mercenary who was killed by a pack of gnolls
